{"tid":1083061,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"湯盈盈45歲前追仔 錢嘉樂攰爆陪買玩具氹女","createTime":"2019-03-29T10:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T11:06:59.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6892af38fb0e02c116ca95c49d624f5f2cd1ef","tid":1083061,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"錢嘉樂、湯盈盈結婚6年4個月，誕下一對可愛女兒，家庭十分美滿，他們更非常恩愛，這天見樂樂疲累不堪，難道晚上太「勤力」？ <br />\n<br />\n日前盈盈、樂樂難得放下女兒去拍拖行街，不過這對廿四孝父母，去購物都是想著女兒，買玩具給她們。湯盈盈似乎是這家店的熟客，甫進內便指示老公到右邊去，夫婦二人很快買完離開，然後盈盈又對放在門口的小恐龍感興趣，似乎是搜羅開派對的道具，屈指一算大女兒凱晴是三月生日的，有機會買來哄她。<br />\n<br />\n其實一直有傳盈盈想趁45歲前，為樂樂追一個慈姑椗，這個大限還有最後倒數兩年，可能是晚晚造人的關係，讓錢嘉樂看來有點疲態？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20190328/480pix/1553769527_657c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20190328%2F480pix%2F1553769527_657c.jpg&h=c15b7b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-mkjkT-DdM8/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F-mkjkT-DdM8%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=9c80d4eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bb5d17b56e739f46203d0bc893febc56ffc298c","tid":1083061,"uid":182127,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"錢七真係醜撚到仆街"},{"pid":"77096566f811ecbe88ee611771053f7cecae3344","tid":1083061,"uid":212704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"生多個好似錢七咁可愛嘅仔就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f478092586a0c3b623db7fe42bb6eb7214e7d44","tid":1083061,"uid":212704,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"錢七係連登女兒<br />\n咁生多個仔 係咪叫連登仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a53404c0eddc5e00e05ed333f4c0ce88aa5c4c","tid":1083061,"uid":35346,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"錢七越黎越似錢家樂，唔知湯盈盈有冇試過叫錯佢做老公呢"}]